data.description: Charming 4 bedroom, 2 bathroom home with freshly painted white brick exterior, boasting spacious living areas and abundant natural light. Modern kitchen, inviting bedrooms, and a serene backyard perfect for relaxation. Home features new wood flooring throughout, recessed lighting installed around the perimeter  of the home, sprinkler system with separate meter, St Augustine lawn, and new storage shed. Prime location with easy access to amenities and schools. Your dream home awaits! Contact you favorite REALTOR® to schedule a private tour TODAY!  Buyer and Buyer's agent to verify accuracy of all information.
